
Getting started with pytram
===========================


STEP 0) Get the package from https://github.com/markovmodel/pytram


STEP 1) Build the extensions using the command

            python setup.py build_ext --inplace


STEP 2) Test the package using the command

            python setup.py test


STEP 3) Run the dTRAM example iPython notebook using the command
        
            ipython notebook dTRAM_example.ipynb

        and have a look how the API works for the given examples


STEP 4) [OPTIONAL] Install and test the package; use

            python setup.py install

        or

            pip install .


STEP 5) [OPTIONAL] Follow these examples and try TRAM with your own application
